<div id="Plaster_Of_Paris_False_Ceiling" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Plaster_Of_Paris_False_Ceiling.jpg" width="500" height="263" alt="Plaster_Of_Paris_False_Ceiling">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Plaster of Paris False Ceiling</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Plaster_Of_Paris_False_Ceiling')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Plaster_Of_Paris_False_Ceiling');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">The Plaster of Paris false ceilings have a high durability and can be shaped and designed as per the requirements.</p>
</div>
<div id="Wooden_False_Ceiling" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Wooden_False_Ceiling.avif" width="500" height="263" alt="Wooden_False_Ceiling">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Wooden False Ceiling</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Wooden_False_Ceiling')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Wooden_False_Ceiling');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">Wood is often used in false ceiling designs due to its natural patterns and textures. Wooden false ceiling gives a warm and rustic look to your room interior. Wooden panels come in the form of hollow blocks, panels, or boards, and plywood.</p>
